content: I'll DM you shortly. I'm copying the link now. But to your question, we're starting off to confirm attendees to the Walz rally in Ashville, NC! Thanks so much for supporting!

did shift from 9-11am -good experience confirming ID attendees were coming 2 rally in NC. stayed on for next shift (which I stayed for part of) & did more calls confirming whether ppl would b attending. then when I got finished w tht I signed out. I had had enough for the moment.  that was a pleasant shift as well. I did the debrief forms but reporting back here cuz I just remembered I think we're sposed to? anyway. it was nice-2 ppl I called thanked ME for volunteering which was kind of them & I appreciated. ðŸ™‚
